# Drizzle: journal MUST be tracked. drizzle-kit migrate (run by
# vercel.json buildCommand) reads meta/_journal.json to know which SQL
# files to apply; excluding it breaks Git-triggered Vercel deploys with
# "Can't find meta/_journal.json file".
